<p>i have written a service in C# to receive json data from android. the below you see what is in the service.</p>  <pre><code>string AddUser(UserInfo info, ResourceInfo resourceInfo); </code></pre>  <p>I am post the JSON Objects to above service in this way. i have tried using jsonArray to put two JSON Objects but it does not work.</p>  <pre><code>private void  postData() throws JSONException, UnsupportedEncodingException {         JSONArray jsonArray = new JSONArray();         JSONObject userInfo = new JSONObject();          userInfo.put("Name", "John");         userInfo.put("status", "Happy");         jsonArray.put(userInfo);          JSONObject resourceinfo = new JSONObject();         resourceinfo.put("filename","abc");         resourceinfo.put("fileEx","jpg");         jsonArray.put(resourceinfo);         invokeWS(jsonArray);         }   private void invokeWS(JSONArray jsonArray) throws UnsupportedEncodingException {          ByteArrayEntity entity = new ByteArrayEntity(jsonArray.toString().getBytes("UTF-8"));         entity.setContentType(new BasicHeader(HTTP.CONTENT_TYPE, "application/json"));         AsyncHttpClient client = new AsyncHttpClient(true, 80, 443);         client.post(getApplicationContext(), "https://abc/adduser", entity, "application/json", new JsonHttpResponseHandler() {             @Override             public void onSuccess(int statusCode, Header[] headers, JSONObject obj) {             Toast.makeText(getApplicationContext(), "" + obj, Toast.LENGTH_LONG).show();                 }                 @Override             public void onFailure(int statusCode, Header[] headers, Throwable throwable, JSONObject errorResponse) {                 if (statusCode == 404) {                     Toast.makeText(getApplicationContext(), "404 - Nie odnaleziono serwera!", Toast.LENGTH_LONG).show();                 } else if (statusCode == 500) {                     Toast.makeText(getApplicationContext(), "500 - Coś poszło nie tak po stronie serwera!", Toast.LENGTH_LONG).show();                 } else if (statusCode == 403) {                     Toast.makeText(getApplicationContext(), "Podano niepoprawne dane!", Toast.LENGTH_LONG).show();                 } else {                     Toast.makeText(getApplicationContext(), throwable.toString(), Toast.LENGTH_LONG).show();                 }             }         });     } </code></pre>  <p>Im try to post the above array to the below service. but it doesn't achieve</p>  <pre><code>string AddUser(UserInfo info, ResourceInfo resourceInfo); </code></pre>